Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 早醬好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(442,436)}上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐你也真是的 故意這樣說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐醬 早醬好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(471,436)}上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早醬好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(424,436}上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒…已經在A班流行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我引導的潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 總是念早醬好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(487,436)}上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會養成壞習慣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 早醬好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(456,436)}上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈…那是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲是「早醬好」反對派
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(439,436)}上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純正美麗的日本語
